events.name: TWICE 5TH WORLD TOUR ‘READY TO BE’ IN JAKARTA
events.description:
ONCE Indonesia! TWICE akan kembali menyapa fans Indonesia lewat tur stadion mereka, TWICE 5TH WORLD TOUR 'READY TO BE' IN JAKARTA.

Konser kali ini merupakan konser TWICE yang kedua di Jakarta, Indonesia.

Grup K-Pop ikonik yang beranggotakan 9 bidadari yaitu, Momo, Jihyo, Sana, Nayeon, Tzuyu, Chaeyoung, Mina, Jeongyeon, dan Dahyun akan memberikan penampilan spesial untuk ONCE Indonesia. Bernyanyi dan berdansa bersama lagu-lagu hits mereka, seperti YES or YES, Fancy, I Can’t Stop Me dan juga lagu-lagu terbaru mereka, SET ME FREE dan MOONLIGHT SUNRISE!

TWICE have stolen your heart, jadi beli tiket konsernya langsung di tiket.com sekarang!

Sampai jumpa di bulan Desember, ONCE~

events.name: LEE JUNHO 1st FANMEETING TOUR (JUNHO THE MOMENT 2023) IN JAKARTA
events.description:
Kabar gembira untuk fans Indonesia Lee Junho! Aktor multi-talenta asal Korea Selatan ini akan hadir di Jakarta untuk acara jumpa fans pertamanya bertajuk LEE JUNHO 1st FANMEETING TOUR <JUNHO THE MOMENT 2023> IN JAKARTA. Aktor dari drama serial ‘King the Land’ dan ‘The Red Sleeve’ ini akan menyapa fans Indonesia di ICE BSD CITY (KAB TANGERANG) Hall 5 pada tanggal 25 November 2023.

Fans Lee Junho juga berkesempatan untuk mengikuti banyak kegiatan Fan Benefit seperti Foto Grup, Sesi Send Off, Event Postcard dan Hadiah Khusus.

Tiket tersedia melalui tiket.com.

Sampai jumpa di bulan November 2023!

events.name: NEO CITY - THE LINK
events.description:
Finally, NCT127 is bringing their ‘NEO CITY : THE LINK’ tour to Jakarta.

Jakarta, Indonesia – Dyandra Global Edutainment is announced to host NCT 127’s solo concert on November 5, 2022, at Indonesia Convention Exhibition (ICE) BSD, Tangerang, Indonesia. The show is part of the boyband’s ‘NEO CITY – THE LINK’ second world tour, which initially began in South Korea in December last year.

After Japan, Singapore, and the Philippines, Indonesia and Bangkok will be their next destination in Asia for the tour. This news is confirmed from NCT 127’s Instagram post that after their Los Angeles, Newark, and Latin America show, Jakarta will be the next stop for NCT 127 2ND TOUR ‘NEO CITY : JAKARTA – THE LINK’.

NCT 127’s Jakarta tour concert will also be fully supported by two big names which appointed the nine-membered group as their brand ambassadors, namely the leading Indonesia leading omnichannel commerce and lifestyle platform Blibli and CLICK as a new toothpaste brand in Indonesia.

Long-established SM Entertainment as artist management and Dream Maker Entertainment as NCT 127 2ND TOUR ‘NEO CITY : JAKARTA – THE LINK’ tour producer will certainly make an epic show, as we all know from their previous artist and show in Indonesia. Thus, this much-anticipated concert will be forever remembered by Indonesian NCTzens.

NCT 127 currently consists of Moon Tae-il, Johnny Suh, Lee Tae-yong, Yuta Nakamoto, Kim Dong-young (Doyoung), Jeong Yun-o (Jaehyun), Kim Jung-woo, Mark Lee, and Lee Dong-hyuck (Haechan). The name NCT is an abbreviation of Neo Culture Technology, while the number 127 is the longitude of the city of Seoul.

Their third and most recent album ‘Sticker’ became the best-selling K-Pop album in 2021, having sold a whopping 3.58 million copies last year. The album has also added another checklist of NCT 127’s achievements by being one of the longest-charting K-Pop artists on the Billboard 200. After making an impressive debut at No. 3, ‘Sticker’ has successfully remained on the chart every week since.

In 2022, the group continued to make history by landing their very first Daesang (Grand Prize) for Artist of the Year at the 31st Seoul Music Awards.

events.name: SMTOWN LIVE 2023 SMCU PALACE @JAKARTA with KB Bank
events.description:
Dyandra Global Edutainment bersama dengan SM Entertainment (SM) dan Dream Maker Entertainment Limited akan menghadirkan konser bertajuk SMTOWN LIVE 2023 SMCU PALACE @JAKARTA with KB Bank di Stadion Gelora Bung Karno, Jakarta pada 23 September 2023 pukul 18.30 WIB. Dengan berkumpulnya jajaran artis naungan SM Entertainment membuat konser ini pastinya sangat ditunggu oleh penggemar di tanah air maupun internasional.

Jakarta akhirnya terpilih kembali sebagai tuan rumah ‘SMTOWN LIVE’ 2023 setelah 11 tahun sejak konser ini terakhir diselenggarakan. Fans dari berbagai penjuru akan menyaksikan langsung penampilan artis-artis SM seperti TVXQ, SUPER JUNIOR, Red Velvet, NCT 127, NCT DREAM, WayV, aespa, dan RIIZE yang memulai debut mereka di bulan September.

Setelah berhasil terselenggaranya ‘SMTOWN LIVE’ di kota-kota besar sejak tahun 2008, konser akbar ini berhasil kembali diadakan tahun lalu di Tokyo Dome setelah tiga tahun vakum. Dengan habis terjualnya tiket untuk tiga hari pertunjukan, termasuk tempat duduk dengan pandangan terbatas, konser ini berhasil menarik lebih dari 150.000 penonton. Pencapaian tersebut memperkuat posisi SMTOWN LIVE sebagai brand pertunjukan global nomor satu.

Dyandra Global Edutainment, along with SM Entertainment (SM) and Dream Maker Entertainment Limited present SMTOWN LIVE 2023 SMCU PALACE @JAKARTA with KB Bank at Gelora Bung Karno Stadium, Jakarta on September 23rd, 2023 at 18:30 Western Indonesian Time (WIB). As the stage is set to assemble exceptional lineups of SM artists, this concert has become the most-awaited show by fans within the nation and worldwide.

Jakarta is finally chosen as the host of ‘SMTOWN LIVE’ 2023 after 11 years since the last time this concert was held. Fans from all over the world will witness the spectacular performances of SM artists such as TVXQ, SUPER JUNIOR, Red Velvet, NCT 127, NCT DREAM, WayV, aespa, and RIIZE whose debut in September.

After undertaking shows in major cities since 2008, ‘SMTOWN LIVE’ made a highly successful comeback last year in Tokyo Dome after a three-year hiatus. With the three-day show selling out, including the restricted view section, the concert attracted more than 150.000 spectators. This accomplishment reaffirms SMTOWN LIVE’s standing as the number one global concert brand.
